	  <description><![CDATA[
	     <div dir="ltr"  trbidi="on"><div class="separator" style="clear: both; text-align: center;"><a href="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QibTxHw4d88/WWUZBOerlwI/AAAAAAAAfCA/MeTSjLHSBvIJzq9sPz7G4bh0clXMWMw-gCLcBGAs/s1600/Akademy2017_banner.png" imageanchor="1" style="margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;"><img border="0" data-original-height="206" data-original-width="840" height="97" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-QibTxHw4d88/WWUZBOerlwI/AAAAAAAAfCA/MeTSjLHSBvIJzq9sPz7G4bh0clXMWMw-gCLcBGAs/s400/Akademy2017_banner.png" width="400" /></a></div><br /><br /><span id="docs-internal-guid-583f1db2-40b7-220c-368a-498bf31af140"></span><br /><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Hi all,</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br class="kix-line-break" /></span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br class="kix-line-break" /></span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">This blog is to assist participants attending the Conference Akademy 2017 at Almeria, Spain.</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br class="kix-line-break" /></span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">There will be a workshop titled "Playing with the amalgam of QML and JavaScript" conducted by me.</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"><br class="kix-line-break" /></span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Timings: 10:30 - 12:15 on 24th July 2017.</span></div><span style="color: #222222; font-family: &quot;verdana&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white; font-size: 12.8px;"><br /></span></span> <span style="color: #222222; font-family: &quot;verdana&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white; font-size: 12.8px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JDD7aiWNWs4/WWUvAtL8vDI/AAAAAAAAfCw/ZtRMnSisIecsAHDcjVl-Dbl34kpP8TbJACK4BGAYYCw/s1600/js-qt.png" imageanchor="1"><img border="0" height="141" src="https://2.bp.blogspot.com/-JDD7aiWNWs4/WWUvAtL8vDI/AAAAAAAAfCw/ZtRMnSisIecsAHDcjVl-Dbl34kpP8TbJACK4BGAYYCw/s320/js-qt.png" width="320" /></a></span></span><br /><span style="color: #222222; font-family: &quot;verdana&quot; , sans-serif;"><span style="background-color: white; font-size: 12.8px;"><br /></span></span><br /><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: white; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Instructions for the </span><span style="background-color: white; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">p</span><span style="background-color: white; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">articipants:</span></div><ul style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 11pt; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">The tutorial will only assume a basic knowledge of using Qt Creator [</span><a href="http://doc.qt.io/qtcreator/index.html" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #1155cc; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">http://doc.qt.io/qtcreator/index.html</span></a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">].</span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 11pt; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">No prior knowledge of QML is required, although it is suggested that attendees be familiar with the </span><a href="http://doc.qt.io/qt-4.8/object.html" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #1155cc; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Objects</span></a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> and JavaScript.</span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; list-style-type: disc; margin-left: 11pt; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">We recommend that the attendees install the </span><a href="https://www.qt.io/download/" style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #1155cc; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: underline; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Qt Creator</span></a><span style="background-color: transparent; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> which includes Qt libraries and compatible compiler. Make sure you are able to build your first "Hello World" project successfully.  </span></div></li></ul><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: white; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">On a side note, please keep in mind of the following advise:</span></div><ul style="margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><li dir="ltr" style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: Arial; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; list-style-type: disc; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Although we do have access to the internet</span><span style="background-color: white; color: #222222; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> for all participants, it is always advised to carry a Data Card or Mobile Internet as a Backup. </span></div></li><li dir="ltr" style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: Georgia; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; list-style-type: disc; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline;"><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Do carry power strip and bring your Laptop Fully charged.</span></div></li></ul><br /><br /><div dir="ltr" style="line-height: 1.38; margin-bottom: 0pt; margin-top: 0pt;"><span style="background-color: transparent; color: black; font-family: &quot;georgia&quot;; font-size: 11pt; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Hope this workshop helps all the participants to get started with building their own QML-JS applications.</span></div></div>

	  ]]></description>
